post0.title: COVID-19 In Washington State
post0.content: UPDATE: The Washington Coronavirus data page got a fresh look and is way nicer now. It's also mysteriously similar to mine ;) Since its very similar to my dashboard, I am not updatng this project any longer. You can go here for the WA data: https://www.doh.wa.gov/emergencies/coronavirus . Total Confirmed Cases: 4310 Total Deaths: 189 updated at: 2020-03-28 .
